{"id": 2941, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪些担忧堪称当代版的“杞人忧天”？", "description": "总有操不完的心。（图片来源：istock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 2798, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190513163338D4lXgiRUySWKIYPj.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-05-13T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 344576, "content": "飞机其他乘客忘记把充电宝从托运行李取出，飞机起火", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897632}, {"id": 345600, "content": "担心所有人都搞同性恋的话会让人类灭绝🙄", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 477519}, {"id": 344577, "content": "每天在担忧明天会发生什么狗屁事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897632}, {"id": 343822, "content": "每天上班考虑吃什么🤔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639623}, {"id": 343837, "content": "担心我们的国家变成第二个日本 韩国 苏联 甚至某某小说中虚构的国家 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746033}, {"id": 343838, "content": "第三次世界大战", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1409352}, {"id": 343840, "content": "有人找你吗？没有\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023014}, {"id": 343845, "content": "以后和老婆在哪里生活😂然而都不知道怎么找GF", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1566593}, {"id": 343849, "content": "毕业后找不到工作怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1584458}, {"id": 343850, "content": "年轻父母担心孩子的起跑线不够高", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913697}, {"id": 344379, "content": "在担心广大贫困人民时，没注意自己其实也是其中之一。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1530915}, {"id": 343870, "content": "假如……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451145}, {"id": 343632, "content": "还没对象，就在想离婚了怎么分割财产，怎么争夺小孩抚养权", "image": null, "praise_count": 124, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288527}, {"id": 343633, "content": "还没三张，就害怕以后能不能适应养老院的环境", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1645999}, {"id": 343634, "content": "没有交往的异性就在关心异性交往情感纠葛", "image": null, "praise_count": 306, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514965}, {"id": 343635, "content": "中了5百万该怎么花…", "image": null, "praise_count": 528, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1598952}, {"id": 343637, "content": "还没多大岁数 就在想自己老了有没有钱看病", "image": null, "praise_count": 117, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512683}, {"id": 343638, "content": "只是喜欢的人和你说几句话，孩子的名字都想好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 243, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703659}, {"id": 343639, "content": "到底是报考清华还是北大？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604219}, {"id": 343640, "content": "还没考上研，就想博士后工资多少", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1652080}, {"id": 343641, "content": "参观大学心里想到自己的孩子还是不要再这里上了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1102747}, {"id": 343642, "content": "跑200米就喘成狗的程度时就担心腿会练粗", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118083}, {"id": 343643, "content": "才刚刚成年已经在担心万一读研出来已经老大不小找不到对象怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626814}, {"id": 343644, "content": "泡沫经济", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1580724}, {"id": 343645, "content": "熬夜担心自己哪天会猝死！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 343646, "content": "中国不用防火墙就要大乱", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 491774}, {"id": 343647, "content": "还没房，就担心房价跌了怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626629}, {"id": 343648, "content": "刚接触一门学科就在想要不要放弃", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551399}, {"id": 343649, "content": "中了五百万税就要交100好桑心", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 446030}, {"id": 343650, "content": "还没开始学，就担心期末考试了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540320}, {"id": 343652, "content": "我这样性格的人，那么挑剔，有时候还有点儿矫情，亲密关系中会给双方带来压力。还是孤独终老好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1385589}, {"id": 343653, "content": "每天疯狂打开手机看消息，其实根本没那么多人找你", "image": null, "praise_count": 331, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 412107}, {"id": 343654, "content": "今年这么特殊，这么多事，考生有这么多，卷子会不会变难，考不好要复读吗，太可怕了，复读生活怎么样的阿", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796123}, {"id": 343655, "content": "上北大好还是清华好", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367589}, {"id": 343656, "content": "因为不婚不育思潮担忧人类灭亡🙄", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 559992}, {"id": 346216, "content": "担心无法建成社会主义、共产主义。担心人类永远走不出太阳系。担心物种过滤器。担心遇见外星人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661020}, {"id": 343658, "content": "担心以三十年后退休了没有养老金", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852421}, {"id": 343660, "content": "房地产泡沫很快会破 。", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038523}, {"id": 343661, "content": "女朋友都没有担心以后自己会不会出轨", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950098}, {"id": 343917, "content": "以等我有钱了作为开场白的一切故事剧本。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626036}, {"id": 343662, "content": "公司没我就要倒了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128392}, {"id": 343669, "content": "环境问题 。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1409352}, {"id": 343675, "content": "刚步入社会、进入职场，就开始忧虑自己会不会秃", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462533}, {"id": 343676, "content": "对于无法改变的事忧心忡忡", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1558597}, {"id": 343677, "content": "没有驾照就天天考虑要买个什么样车", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609666}, {"id": 343678, "content": "还没有出名就开始考虑某天出名了该怎样怎样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648050}, {"id": 343680, "content": "毕业找不找的着工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618604}, {"id": 343681, "content": "担心外星人入侵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1628566}, {"id": 345987, "content": "量子力学😄", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1659002}, {"id": 343687, "content": "我要是练成施瓦辛格那样该怎么办啊\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1652162}]}